reviewText: I really liked this video I just wish they had spent more time and gone into more detail..but still worth watching

I sent this to a friend in Ireland who was thinking about visiting my neck of the woods, and even though I haven't viewed this DVD, it must be good, because we will be expecting our Irish friends to visit in a couple of years. :-)  We are going to visit THEM next year!  We've seen several of Rudy's programs on PBS, so we know the quality of his travel shows already.  Based on that, I'd recommend this one!
